OL,7,FA Scottish father who stepped in front
OL,8,Fof a train with his two-year-old son
OL,9,Fhas been jailed for ten years.
OL,11,FFrederick Danquah was carrying his
OL,12,Fyoung son when he stepped in front of
OL,13,Fa train at Garrowhill railway station
OL,14,Fin Glasgow in July 2023 after an
OL,15,Fargument with the child's mother.
OL,17,FThe 28-year-old sustained a broken jaw
OL,18,Fand neck fracture, while the boy
OL,19,Fsuffered cuts and bruises.
