OL,7,FThe toddler was discharged from
OL,8,Fhospital two days later.
OL,10,FIn sentencing Danquah, Judge Tony
OL,11,FKelly said the "harm was of the
OL,12,Fgreatest kind".
OL,14,F"To seek to take the life of your son
OL,15,Fover some hours is great criminality,"
OL,16,Fhe said.
OL,18,F"I have no doubt about your
OL,19,Fintentions: you meant to have his
OL,20,Fmother attend his funeral.
