OL,7,F"There were opportunities to place
OL,8,Fyour son in the care of others,
OL,9,Finstead you took him with you.
OL,11,F"You require to be punished."
OL,13,FThe judge has also ordered a non-
OL,14,Fharassment order until the child turns
OL,15,F18.
OL,17,FThe court heard it was not just the
OL,18,Fboy and his family that had been
OL,19,Faffected by this crime, but the train
OL,20,Fdrivers and rescuers who had
OL,21,Fexperienced "various stages of upset".
