OL,7,FThe court also heard Danquah's ex-
OL,8,Fpartner had written to the judge
OL,9,Foffering a "substantial degree of
OL,10,Fsupport", including "confirmation of
OL,11,Fhis relationship with his child".
OL,13,FFollowing the sentencing, DCI Marc
OL,14,FFrancey from the British Transport
OL,15,FPolice said Danquah's actions were
OL,16,F"incomprehensible" and "abhorrent".
OL,18,F"He deliberately put a young child's
OL,19,Flife in extreme danger and it is only
OL,20,Fthrough sheer luck that he wasn't
OL,21,Fseriously injured or killed," he said.
